subTiles.displayName: Transaction Execution Times and Milestones Chronology
Tracking Fields and Values Grouped by Transactions

dashboards.description: Provides business process tracking and monitoring based on tracking fields created in your Integrations.

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Record Type' = 'insights record' | timestats count(Action) as Milestones by Action

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Record Type' = 'insights record' | link 'OPC Request ID', 'Transaction ID' | rename 'Group Duration' as 'Transaction Time' | sequence name = Milestones [ Action != null and 'Action Type' != null and 'Event ID' != null ]{1,} select Action, 'Action Type', 'Event ID', Integration | stats latest(Integration) as Integration, latest(Action) as 'Latest Action', unique('Project ID') as 'Project Name', distinctcount(Identifier) as Integrations, unique(Entity) as Entity, unique(Instance) as Instance | rename Count as 'Step Count' | classify correlate = -*, Integration, 'Latest Action', 'Project Name', Integrations 'Start Time', 'Transaction ID', 'Step Count', 'Transaction Time' as 'Transaction Execution Time' | fields target = ui -'OPC Request ID', -Entity, -Instance, -'Start Time', -'End Time', -Entity

'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and [ Key like '*' and Value like '*' | distinct 'Transaction ID' ] | link 'Transaction ID', Key, Value | eventstats latest('Project ID') as 'Project Name', earliest('Start Time') as 'Started at', latest('End Time') as 'Last Action Time', latest(Integration) as Integration | createtable name = 'Request Summary' select 'Transaction ID', 'Project Name', 'Started at', literal(exception) as 'Selected Action', Integration as 'Integration Name', Key as 'Tracking Field', Value as 'Tracking Field Value'

LINK_SEARCH_SETTINGS.linkSummaryInput: <title-text>OIC Service Instances</title-text> <title-text>Projects</title-text> <title-text>Total Integrations</title-text> <title-text>Transactions</title-text> <title-text>Integration Instances</title-text> <title-text>Milestones</title-text>

uiConfig.queryString: 'Log Source' = 'OCI Integration Activity Stream Logs' and 'Record Type' = 'insights record' | link Entity | addfields [ 'Project ID' = null and Identifier != null | stats distinctcount(Identifier) as 'standalone-integs' ] | stats count(Action) as 'Total Actions' | eventstats distinctcount(Entity) as 'OIC Service Instances', distinctcount('Project ID') as 'Unique Projects', distinctcount('OPC Request ID') as 'Unique Transactions', distinctcount(Identifier) as 'Unique Integrations', distinctcount(Instance) as 'Instance Execs', sum('standalone-integs') as 'Standalone Integrations' | fields -Count, -'standalone-integs', -'Start Time', -'End Time'
